hadiths[66]{hadithnumber,text}:
3827,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala sey dua nahin karta , Allah is par naraz hota hai."
3828,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dua hi ibadat hai. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ye aayat padhi : ( وَقَالَ رَبُّکُمُ ادْعُوْنِیۡ اَسْتَجِبْ لَکُمْ ), ''aur tumharey Rab ney farmaya : mujhey pukaro, main tumhari pukar qubul karunga.''"
3829,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala key yahan dua sey badh kar koi chiz izzat wali nahin."
3830,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni dua mein farmaya kartey they : ( رَبِّ أَعِنِّي وَلَا تُعِنْ عَلَيَّ . . وَاسْلُلْ سَخِيمَةَ قَلْبِي ), ''aey merey Rab ! meri madad farma, aur merey khilaf (dushman ki) madad na farma, aur meri taeed farma, aur merey khilaf (dushman ki) taeed na farma, aur merey haq mein tadbeer farma, aur merey khilaf tadbeer na farma, aur mujhey hidayat dey, aur hidayat ko merey liye aasan kar dey, aur jo mujh par ziyadti karey uskey khilaf meri madad farma, aey merey Rab ! mujhey aisa (banda) bana jo tera bahut shukar karney wala ho, tera bahut zikr karney wala ho, tujh sey bahut darney wala ho, teri itaat karney wala ho, terey samney aajizi karney wala ho, teri taraf hi ro-ro kar ruju karney wala (aur tauba karney wala) ho. aey merey Rab ! meri tauba qubul farma, merey gunah dho dal, meri dua qubul kar, merey dil ko hidayat dey, meri zaban sidhi rakh, meri daleel ko (pukhta aur) qaaim rakh, aur merey dil sey keena nikal dey. Abul-Hasan Tanaafusi (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mainey Wakee (Rahimahullah) sey kaha : kya main witr mein ye duayen mang liya karun? unhoney farmaya : haan."
3831,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anhuma) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar eik khaadima Ata farmaney ki darkhaast ki to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un sey farmaya : merey paas to (ghulam ya londi) nahin hai jo tujhey dey sakoon. wo wapis chali gaeen. baad mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unkey yahan tashrif ley gaey aur farmaya : kya tujhey wo chiz pasand hai jo tu ney maangi thi ya wo jo us sey behtar hai? Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney un sey kaha : kaho : nahin, wo chiz (matloob hai) jo is sey behtar hai. Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney yehi jawab dey diya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : yun kaha kar : (اَللّٰھُمَّ رَبَّ السَّمَاوَاتِ السِّبْعِ . . وَأَعْنِنَامِنَ الْفَقْرِ), ''aey Allah ! aey saton aasmano key Malik ! aey arshe-azeem key Malik ! aey hamarey Rab aur har chiz key Rab ! aey Toraat, Injeel aur Quraane-Azeem key nazil karney waley ! to awwal hai, tujh sey pehley kuchh nahin tha. to aakhir hai, terey baad kuchh nahin. to zahir hai, tujh sey ooper kuchh nahin. to baatin (poshida) hai, tujh sey poshida tar kuch nahin. hamara qarz ada farma aur faqr sey (najat dey kar) hamein ghani kar dey."
3832,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : (اَللّٰھُمَّ اِنِّی أَسْأَلُكَ الْھُدٰی وَالتُّقٰی وَالْعَفَافَ وَالْغِنٰی), ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey hidayat, taqwa, paak damani aur istighnaa (beniyaazi) ka sawal karta hun.''"
3833,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : (اَللّٰھُمَّ ! انْفَعْنِی بِمَا عَلَّمْتَنِی , وَعَلِّمْنِی مَایَنْفَعُنِی , وَزِدنِی عِلْمًا , وَالْحَمْدُلِلّٰہِ عَلٰی کُلِّ حَالٍ , وَاَعُوْذُبِاللہِ مِنْ عَذَابِ النَّارِ), ''aey Allah ! tu ney mujhey jo ilm diya hai us sey mujhey faeyda dey, aur mujhey wo ilm ata farma jo mujhey faeyda dey aur merey ilm mein izafa farma. har haal mein Allah ki tareef hai aur main aag key azab sey Allah ki panah ka Talib hun.''"
3834,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kasrat sey farmaya kartey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ ثَبِّتْ قَلْبِي عَلَى دِينِكَ ), ''aey Allah ! merey dil ko apney Deen par qaaim rakh."" eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya aap ko hamarey barey mein (gumrah honey ka) khatra hai? halanke hum aap par eman la chukey hain aur jo kuchh (emaan aur amal key ehkam) aap laye hain, in ko sach mantey hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dil Rahmaan ki do ungliyon key darmiyan hain, wo unhen tabdeel karta rehta hai. Imam Aamash (Rahimahullah) ney ye hadees bayan kartey huye do ungliyon sey ishara kiya."
3835,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey arz kiya ke mujhey koi dua sikhaein jo main namaz mein manga karun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aap yun kaha karen : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي ظَلَمْتُ نَفْسِي ظُلْمًا كَثِيرًا وَلَا يَغْفِرُ الذُّنُوبَ إِلَّا أَنْتَ فَاغْفِرْ لِي مَغْفِرَةً مِنْ عِنْدِكَ وَارْحَمْنِي إِنَّكَ أَنْتَ الْغَفُورُ الرَّحِيمُ), ''aey Allah ! mainey apni jaan par bahut zulm kiya hai aur terey siwa koi gunahon ko maaf nahin karta, apney paas sey meri maghfirat farma aur mujh par rehmat farma, bila shubha to hi bahut bakhshney wala, nihayat reham karney wala hai.''"
3836,"Hazrat Abu-Umama Baahli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney asaa key saharey hamarey paas tashrif laye. jab hamney aap ko dekha to (aehatraman) khadey ho gaey. aap ney farmaya : is tarah na karo jis tarah Faarsi log apney sardaron key sath kartey hain. hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap hamarey liye dua farmaai . aap ney farmaya : (اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْ لَنَا وَارْحَمْنَا وَارْضَ عَنَّا وَتَقَبَّلْ مِنَّا وَأَدْخِلْنَا الْجَنَّةَ وَنَجِّنَا مِنْ النَّارِ وَأَصْلِحْ لَنَا شَأْنَنَا كُلَّهُ), ''aey Allah ! hamari maghfirat farma, hum par rehmat farma, hum sey razi ho ja, hamari duayen qubul farma, hamein jannat mein dakhil farma, hamein jahannam sey najat dey aur hamarey sarey kaam sanwaar dey.'' hum ney mazeed dua key liye khahish ka izhar kiya to aap ney farmaya : kya mainey tumharey liye sab kuch jama nahin kar diya?"
3837,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنْ الْأَرْبَعِ مِنْ عِلْمٍ لَا يَنْفَعُ وَمِنْ قَلْبٍ لَا يَخْشَعُ وَمِنْ نَفْسٍ لَا تَشْبَعُ وَمِنْ دُعَاءٍ لَا يُسْمَعُ), ''aey Allah ! main chaar chizon sey teri panah chahta hun is ilm sey jo faeyda na dey, us dil sey jis mein aajizi na ho, us nafs sey jo sair na ho aur us dua sey jo suni na jaaey."
3838,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) in alfaz key sath dua manga kartey they : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ فِتْنَةِ النَّارِ وَعَذَابِ النَّارِ . . وَالْمَأْثَمِ وَالْمَغْرَمِ), 'aey Allah ! main teri panah mein aata hun (jaham ki) aag ki aazmaaish aur (jahannam ki) aag key azab sey, qabr ki aazmaaish aur qabr key azab sey, dolat ki aazmaaish key shar sey aur muflisi ki aazmaaish key shar sey aur Masih Dajjaal ki aazmaaish key shar sey, aey Allah ! meri ghaltiyon ko barf aur olon key pani sey dho dal, aur merey dil ko gunahon sey isi tarah paak kar dey jis tarah to safed kapdey ko mail-kuchail sey saaf kar deta hai, merey aur merey gunahon key darmiyan isi tarah doori kar dey jis tarah tu ney mashriq aur maghrib ko eik doosrey sey door kar diya hai, ya Allah ! main teri panah mein aata hun susti sey, intehai budhapey sey, gunah aur tawaan (jurmaane) sey."
3839,"Hazrat Farwa bin Naufal Ashjai (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki dua key barey mein sawal kiya, jo aap maangtey rahey hon. Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : (اللهم إِنِّي أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنْ شَرِّ ما عَمِلْتُ وَمِنْ شَرِّ ما لَمْ أَعْمَلْ), ''aey Allah ! main us amal key shar sey teri panah mein aata hun jo mainey kiya aur us amal key shar sey bhi jo mainey nahin kiya.''"
3840,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein ye dua is tarah sikhatey they jis tarah Quran Majeed ki sura sikhatey they : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ . . مِنْ فِتْنَةِ الْمَحْيَا وَالْمَمَاتِ), ''aey Allah ! main jahannam key azab sey teri panah maangta hun, aur qabr key azab sey teri panah ka Talib hun, aur Masih Dajjaal key fitney sey teri panah mein aata hun, aur tujh sey zindagi aur maut key fitney sey panah maangta hun."
3841,"Ummul-mominin sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik raat mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aap key bistar par na paya, chunanche mainey (andherey mein tatol kar) talash kiya to mera haath Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key qadmon key talwon par pada jo khadey they. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz ki jagah mein (sar-basjood) they aur farma rahey they : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي . . أَنْتَ كَمَا أَثْنَيْتَ عَلَى نَفْسِكَ), ''aey Allah ! main teri narazi sey teri khushnoodi ki panah mein aata hun, teri saza sey teri maafi ki panah mein aata hun, aur tujh sey teri panah mein aata hun, main teri puri tarah tareef nahin kar sakta, to wesey hi hai jaisey tu ney apni tareef khud farmaai.''"
3842,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : faqr, qillat, zillat, zulm karney aur mazloom honey sey Allah ki panah maango."
3843,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah sey nafa bakhsh ilm maango aur faeyda na deney waley ilm sey Allah ki panah maango."
3844,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) buzdili, bukhl, intehai budhapey aur laachaari ki Umar, azabe-qabr aur seeney key fitney sey panah manga kartey they. Imam Wakee (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : seeney (aur dil) key fitney sey murad ye hai ke aadmi fitney mein mubtala ho kar faut ho jaey aur usney Allah sey (bachney key liye) us sey maafi na maangi ho."
3845,"Hazrat Tariq bin Ashim Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna jabke eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! jab main apney Rab sey sawal karun to kaisey karun? aap ney farmaya : is tarah keh : (اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْلِي وَارْحَمْنِي وَعَافِنِي وَارْزُقْنِي), ''ya-Allah ! mujhey bakhsh dey, mujh par reham kar, mujhey aafiyat dey aur mujhey rizq dey."" aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (ye farmatey huye) angoothey key siwa chaaron ungliyan ikhatti kin (chaar ka ishara kiya) aur farmaya : ye kalimaat terey liye terey Deen aur teri duniya (ki bhalaiyan) sametey huye hain."
3846,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen ye dua sikhai : (اللّهم ! إني أَسأَلك . خيرًا), ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey har qism ki khair maangta hun, jaldi milney wali aur der sey milney wali (ya duniya ki aur aakhirat ki), wo bhi jis ka mujhey ilm hai aur wo bhi jis ka mujhey ilm nahin. aey Allah ! main har qism key shar sey teri panah mein aata hun, jaldi aaney waley sey bhi, aur der sey aaney waley sey bhi (ya duniya aur aakhirat key shar sey), jis ka mujhey ilm hai, us sey bhi aur jis ka mujhey ilm nahin, us sey bhi. ya-Allah ! main tujh sey wo khair maangta hun jo tujh sey terey bandey aur terey Nabi (Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) ney maangi hai. aur main us shar sey teri panah mein aata hun jis shar sey terey bandey aur terey Nabi (Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) ney panah maangi hai. ya Allah ! main tujh sey jannat ka sawal karta hun aur har us qol aur amal (ki tofiq) ka sawal karta hun jo us sey qarib kerey. aur main (jahannam ki) aag sey teri panah mein aata hun aur har us qol aur amal sey panah maangta hun jo us (jahannam) sey qarib karey. aur main ye sawal karta hun ke to jo bhi faisla karey usey merey liye behtar (ya khair ka baais) bana dey."
3847,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi sey puchha : tum namaz mein kya padhtey ho?  usney kaha : main tashahud ataehiyaat padhta hun, phir Allah sey jannat ka sawal karta hun aur (jahannam ki) aag sey uski panah maangta hun. qism hai Allah ki ! mujhey aap jaisi ya Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) jaisi gungunaahat nahin aati. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hum bhi unhi (dono) key barey mein gungunaatey (sawal kartey) hain."
3848,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kon si dua afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : apney Rab sey duniya aur aakhirat mein maafi aur aafiyat ka sawal kar. phir wo aadmi aap key paas doosrey din khidmat mein hazir huwa aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kon si dua afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : apney Rab sey duniya aur aakhirat mein maafi aur aafiyat ka sawal kar. phir wo teesrey din khidmat mein hazir huwa aur kaha : aey Allah key Nabi ! kon si dua afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney Rab sey duniya aur aakhirat mein maafi aur aafiyat ka sawal kar. jab tujhey duniya aur aakhirat mein maafi aur aafiyat mil jaaeygi to yaqinan to kamiyab ho jaeyga."
3849,"Hazrat Osat bin Ismail Bijli (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat key baad Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye farmatey suna : guzishta saal Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is maqam par khadey huye jahan main khada hun. phir (ye keh kar) Abu-Bakar aankho mein aansoo aa gaey. aur farmaya ! phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya tha : sach ikhtiyar karo, wo neki key sath hota hai, aur wo dono (sach aur neki aur unhen ikhtiyar karney waley) jannat mein hongey. aur jhoot sey bach kar raho, wo gunah key sath hota hai, aur wo dono (jhoot aur gunah aur unhen ikhtiyar karney waley) jahannam mein hongey. aur Allah sey aafiyat ka sawal karo. kisi ko yaqin (aur emaan) key baad aafiyat sey behtar koi chiz nahin mil sakti. eik doosrey sey hasad na karo. eik doosrey sey bughz na rakho. eik doosrey sey qata' talluq na karo. eik doosrey sey munh na modon, aur Allah key bando ! bhai bhai bin jaao."
3850,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! agar main Lailatulqadr paa lun to kya dua maangun? aap ney farmaya : yun kehna : (اللّهُمَّ إِنَّكَ عَفُوٌّ تُحِبُّ الْعَفْوَ فَاعْفُ عنِّي), ''aey Allah ! to bahut ziyada maaf karney wala hai, to maaf karna pasand karta hai, lihaza mujhey maaf farma dey.''"
3851,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : banda jo bhi dua maangta hai wo is dua sey afzal nahin hoti : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَسْأَلُكَ الْمُعَافَاةَ فِي الدُّنْيَا وَالْآخِرَةِ), ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey duniya aur aakhirat mein aafiyat ka sawal karta hun.''"
3852,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala hum par aur qome-Aad ki hum nasab shakhsiyat (Hazrat Hud (Alaihissalam)) par reham farmaaey."
3853,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey eik ki dua qubul hoti rehti hai jab tak ke wo jald bazi na kerey. arz kiya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! wo jald bazi kis tarah karta hai? aap ney farmaya : wo kehta hai : mainey Allah sey dua ki lekin Allah ney meri dua qubul nahin ki."
3854,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs yun na kahey : ya Allah ! agar to chahta hai to mujhey bakhsh dey. usey chahiye ke pukhta ummid key sath dua maangey kyonkey Allah ko koi majbur nahin kar sakta."
3855,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazeed (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ka azeem tareen naam (Isme-Azam) in do aayaton mein hai : (وَاِلٰهُكُمْ اِلٰهٌ وَّاحِدٌ لَّا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا هُوَ الرَّحْمٰنٌ الرَّحِيْمُ), ''tumhara mabood eik hi mabood hai, uskey siwa koi mabood nahin jo nihayat meharban, behad reham karney wala hai.'' aur Sura Aale-Imran key shuru mein (yani)  (الٓمّ اللهُ لآ اِلٰهَ اَلَّا هُوَ الْحَيُّ الْقَيُّوْمُ)."
3856,"Hazrat Qasim bin Abdur-Rehman Dimashqi (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Allah ka azeem tareen naam (Isme-Azam) jis key sath Allah sey dua ki jaey to wo qubul farmata hai, teen Suraton mein hai : Sura Baqra , Sura Aale-Imran aur Sura Taa-Haa mein. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney mazkura baala riwayat apney ustaad Abdur-Rehman bin Ibrahim Dimashqi (Rahimahullah) sey eik dusri sanad sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey marfoo bhi isi tarah bayan ki hai."
3857,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko yun kehtey suna : (اللّٰهم إِني أَسأَلك . . . . . . . أَحدٌ), ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey sawal karta hun, isliye ke to Allah hai, akela hai, be-niyaz hai jisney kisi ko janm nahin diya hai, aur na hi usey kisi ney janm diya, na uska koi hum-sar hai.'' to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is shakhs ney Allah sey uskey azeem tareen naam (Isme-Azam) key waseeley sey sawal kiya hai jis key waseeley sey jab us sey manga jaey to wo ata farmata hai aur jab uskey waseeley sey us sey dua ki jaey to wo qubul farmata hai."
3858,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko suna , wo keh raha tha : ( اللّٰهُمَّ إِنِّي أّسْألُكَ . . ذُوالْجَلَالِ وَالإِكْرامِ ), ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey is waseeley sey sawal karta hun ke tareef sirf terey liye hai, tujh akeley key siwa koi mabood nahin, tera koi shareek nahin, to ehsan karney wala hai, aasmano aur zamin ko baghair misal key paida karney wala hai, jalal aur izzat wala hai."" to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : usney Allah sey uskey azeem-tareen naam (Isme-Azam) key wastey sey sawal kiya hai jis key waseeley sey manga jaey to wo ata farmata hai aur jab uskey waseeley sey dua ki jaey to wo qubul farmata hai."
3859,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna , aap farma rahey they : (اللّٰهم إني أسألك . . . . . . . . فرَّجت), ''ya Allah ! main tujh sey terey us taahir, paak, barkat waley aur tujhey sab sey piyarey naam key wastey sey sawal karta hun jis key waseeley sey jab tujh sey dua ki jaey to to qubul farmata hai, aur jab tujh sey uskey waseeley sey kuchh manga jaey to to ata farmata hai, aur jab tujh sey uskey wastey sey rehmat talab ki jaey to to rehmat farmata hai, aur jab tujh sey uskey wastey sey pareshani door karney ki darkhaast ki jaey to to pareshani door karta (aur mushkil kashaai farmata) hai.'' (baad mein) eik din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Aaisha ! tujhey pata hai Allah Taala ney mujhey wo naam bata diya hai jis key wastey sey jab usey pukara jaey to wo qubul farmata hai? mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! merey maa baap aap par qurban ! mujhey bhi sikha dijiye. aap ney farmaya : aey Aaisha ! wo terey liye munasib nahin. unhoney kaha : main kuch der eik taraf bethi rahi, phir main uthi aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sar Mubarak ko bosa dey kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey sikha dijiye. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey Aaisha ye baat tumharey liye munasib nahin ke main tumhen wo sikhaaun. tumharey liye munasib nahin ke uskey waseeley sey duniya ki koi chiz maango. Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : mainey uth kar wuzu kiya, phir do rakat namaz padhi, phir mainey kaha : (اللّٰهم ! إني أَدعوك اللهَ . وترحمني), ''ya Allah ! main tujhey Allah kehti hun, main tujhey Rahmaan key naam sey pukaarti hun, main tujhey barrur-raheem pukaarti hun, main tujhey terey tamam behtareen namon ka wasta deti hun jo naam mujhey malum hain aur jo malum nahin (un sab namon ka wasta dey kar dua karti hun) ke meri maghfirat farma dey aur mujh par rehmat farma dey. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain : phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khub hansey aur farmaya : wo unhin namon mein hai jinkey waseeley sey tu ney dua ki hai."
3860,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key ninnanwey, yani eik kam sau naam hain, jo unhen shumar kerega, jannat mein dakhil ho jaeyga."
3861,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala key ninnanwey, yani eik kam sau naam hain. wo akela hai aur taaq adad ko pasand karta hai. jo shakhs unhein yad kerega, jannat mein dakhil hoga. wo ye hain : (اَللہ) mabood, (اَلْوَاحِد) eik, (اَلصَّمَد ) beniyaz, (اَلاَوَّل) sab sey pehley mojud,  (اَلْآخِرُ) sab key baad rehney wala, (اَلظَّاهِرُ) apni qudrat ke lihaaz se zaahir, (اَلْبَاطِنُ) apni haqiqat key lihaz sey poshida, (اَلْخَالِقُ) paida karney wala, (اَلْبَارِیءُ) bananey wala, ( اَلْمُصَوِّرُ ) soorten bananey wala, ( اَلْمَالِكُ ) badshah, ( اَلْحَقُّ ) sacha, ( اَلسَّلاَمُ ) salamti wala, ( اَلْمُؤْمِنُ ) aman deney wala, ( اَلْمُھَیْمِنُ ) nigehban, ( اَلْعَزِیْزُ ) ghalib, ( اَلْجَبَّارُ ) zabardast ya kami puri karney wala, ( اَلْمُتَکَبِّرُ ) apni azmat ka izhar karney wala, ( اَلرَّحْمٰنُ ) intehai reham karney wala, ( اَلرَّحِیْمُ ) hamesha reham karney wala, ( اَللَّطِیْفُ ) bareek dekhnewala, ( اَلْخَبِیْرُ ) hamesha ba-khabar, ( اَلسَّمِیْعُ ) khub sunney wala, ( اَلْبَصِیْرُ ) khub dekhney wala, ( اَلْعَلِیْمُ ) khub jaan'ney wala, ( اَلْعَظِیْمُ ) khub azmat wala, ( اَلْبَارُّ ) ehsan karney wala, ( اَلْمُتَعَالُ ) buland, ( اَلْجَلِيْلُ ) pad aur jalal wala, ( اَلْجَمِیْلُ ) sahibe-jamaal, ( اَلْحَیُّ ) zinda, ( اَلْقَیُّوْمُ ) qaaim rehney aur qaaim rakhney wala, ( اَلْقَادِرُ ) sab kuchh kar sakney wala, ( اَلْقَاھِرُ ) ghalib, ( اَلْعَلِیُّ ) bahut buland, ( اَلْحَکِیْمُ ) khub hikmaton wala, ( اَلْقَرِیْبُ ) ilm aur qudrat key lihaz sey makhluq sey intehai qarib, ( اَلْمُجِیْبُ ) qubul karney wala, ( اَلْغَنِیُّ ) be parwah jo kisi ka mohtaj nahin, ( اَلْوَهَّابُ ) bahut kuchh deney wala, ( اَلْوَدُوْدُ ) bahut ziyada mohabbat rakhney wala mehboob, ( اَلشَّکُوْرُ ) nihayat qadardan, ( اَلْمَاجِدُ ) buzurgi wala, ( اَلْوَاجِدُ ) aisa ghani jo kabhi muflis aur mohtaj na ho, ( اَلْوَالِیُّ ) Malik aur mukhtaar, ( اَلرَّاشِدُ ) hidayat deney wala, ( اَلْعَفَوُّ ) bahut ziyada maaf karney wala, ( اَلْغَفُوْرُ ) bahut gunah bakhshney wala, ( اَلْحَلِیْمُ ) hamesha darguzar karney wala, ( اَلْکَرِیْمُ ) be-inteha sakhi, har qism ki sifaat kamaal rakhnewala, ( اَلتَّوَّابُ ) bahut ziyada tauba qubul karney wala, ( اَلرَّبُّ ) Malik, paalney wala, ( الْمَجِيدُ ) hamesha rehne wala buzurgi wala, ( اَلْوَلِیُّ ) madadgar, ( اَلشَّھِیْدُ ) gawahi deney wala, (اَلْمُبِیْنُ ) wazeh karney wala, ( اَلْبُرْهَانُ ) daleel, ( اَلرَّؤُوْفُ ) bahut shafqat karney wala, ( اَلرَّحِیْمُ ) hamesha reham karney wala, ( اَلِمُبْدِئُ ) pehli baar paida karney wala, ( اَلْمُعِیْدُ ) dobara paida karney wala, ( اَلْبَاعِثُ ) qabron sey uthaney wala, ( اَلْوَارِثُ ) waris (baqi rehney wala), ( اَلْقَوِیُّ ) bahut ziyada quwat wala, ( اَلشَّدِیْدُ ) sakhti karney wala, (اَلضَّارُ) nuqsan ka ikhtiyar rakhney wala, ( اَلنَّافِعُ ) nafa pahunchaney wala, ( اَلْبَاقِیُّ ) hamesha baqi rehney wala, (اَلْوَاقِیُّ ) bachaney wala, mehfooz rakhney wala, (اَلْخَافِضُ ) past karney wala, (اَلرَّافِعُ) buland karney wala, (اَلْقَابِضُ ) tangi karney wala, ( الْبَاسِطُ ) faraakhi karney wala, (اَلْمُعِزُّ) izzat deney wala, (اَلْمُذِلُّ ) zillat deney wala, (اَلْمُقْسِطُ) insaf karney wala, (اَلرَزَّاقُ ) rizq deney wala, (ذُوالْقُوَّۃِ) quwat wala, (اَلْمَتِیْنُ) nihayat mazboot, (اَلْقَائِمُ) hamesha rehney wala, ( اَلدَّئِمُ ) hameshgii wala, ( اَلْحَافِظُ ) hifazat karney wala, ( اَلْوَکِیْلُ ) karsaz, ( اَلْفَاطِرُ ) paida karney wala, ( اَلسّامِعُ ) sunney wala, ( اَلْمُعْطِیُّ ) deney wala, ( اَلْمُحْيِی ) zindagi bakhshney wala, ( اَلْمُمِیْتُ ) maut deney wala, ( اَلْمَانِعُ ) rokney wala, ( اَلْجَامِعُ ) jama karney wala, ( اَلْھَادِیُّ ) hidayat deney wala rehnumaai karney wala, (اَلْکَافِي) kifaayat karney wala, (اَلّاَبَدُ) hameshgi wala, ( اَلْعَالِمُ ) janney wala, (اَلصَّادِقُ) sacha, (اَلنُّوْرُ) roshan, (اَلْمُنِیْرُ) roshni karney wala, (اَلتَّامُ) mukammal, ( اَلْقَدِيْمُ ) puraana, (اَلْوِتْرُ) eik, ( اَلْاَحَدُ ) akela, (اَلصَّمَدُ) be-niyaz, (الذی لَمْ يَلِدْ وَلَمْ يُولَدْ وَلَمْ يَكُن لَّهُ كُفُوًا أَحَدٌ ) jisney na kisi ko janm diya na usey kisi ney janm diya na uska koi hum sar hi hai. Zuhair bin Tameemi (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : hamein mutaaddid (bahut se) ulama ka ye qol malum huwa hai ke asmaye husnaa shuru kartey waqt pehley ye kehna chahiye : (لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ , لَهُ الْمُلْكُ وَلَهُ الْحَمْدُ , بِيَدِهِ الْخَيْرُ وَهُوَ عَلَى كُلِّ شَيْءٍ قَدِيرٌ , لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ , لَهُ الْأَسْمَاءُ الْحُسْنَى), ''akeley Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, usi ka koi shareek nahin, badshahi usi ki hai aur tareef bhi usi ki hai usi key haath mein sari bhalai hai aur wo har chiz par khub qadir hai, Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, usi key behtareen naam hain.''"
3862,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen duayen qubul hotin hain. un (ki qubuliyat) mein koi shak nahin : mazloom ki dua, musafir ki dua aur walid ki apni aulad key haq mein dua."
3863,"Hazrat Umme Hakim binte Wadaa' Khuzaa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (maa) baap ki dua (Allah taala key) hijaab tak pahunch jati hai (qubul hoti hai)."
3864,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney apney betey ko (dua mein) yun kehtey suna : aey Allah : main tujh sey darkhaast karta hun ke jab main jannat mein dakhil hun to mujhey jannat mein daain taraf safed mehal dena. unhoney farmaya : betey ! Allah sey jannat maango aur (jahannam ki) aag sey uski panah maango kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai, aap farma rahey they : aainda aisey log hongey jo dua mein had sey aage badh jaaya karengey."
3865,"Hazrat Salman Faarsi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara parwardigar haya-daar aur sakhi hai. wo is baat sey sharmata hai ke banda (dua key liye) uski taraf haath uthaey aur wo unhein khaali, ya farmaya : na kaam pher dey."
3866,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to Allah sey dua karey to hatheliyon ko andar ki taraf ooper kar key dua kar, haathon ki pusht key sath dua na kar. jab to (dua sey) farigh ho jaey to haathon ko chehrey par pher ley."
3867,"Hazrat Abu Ayaash Zarqi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs subah key waqt yun kehta hai : (لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ لَهُ الْمُلْكُ وَلَهُ الْحَمْدُ وَهُوَ عَلَى كُلِّ شَيْءٍ قَدِيرٌ), ''akeley Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, uska koi shareek nahin, badshahi usi ki hai, aur tareef bhi usi ki hai, aur wo har chiz par khub qadir hai. usey Hazrat Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki aulad mein sey eik ghulam azad karney ka sawab milega. uskey das gunah maaf ho jaeyngey. uskey das darjey buland ho jaeyngey, aur wo Sham tak shetan sey mehfooz rahega. agar Sham ko kahey to yehi sawab hoga aur subah tak (shetan sey) mehfooz rahega. eik aadmi ko khuwab mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ziyaarat hui to usney (khuwab mein) arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! Abu Ayaash aap sey is tarah (mazkoora) hadees riwayat kartey hain. aap ney farmaya : Abu Ayaash sach kehta hai."
3868,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab subah ho jaey to kaho : ( اللَّهُمَّ بِكَ أَصْبَحْنَا وَبِكَ أَمْسَيْنَا وَبِكَ نَحْيَا وَبِكَ نَمُوتُ ), ''aey Allah ! hamney teri tofiq sey subah ki aur teri inayat sey Sham ki, aur teri qudrat sey hum zinda hain aur teri qudrat hi sey mareingey.'' aur jab Sham ho jaey to kaho : (اللَّهُمَّ بِكَ أَمْسَيْنَا وَبِكَ أَصْبَحْنَا وَبِكَ نَحْيَا وَبِكَ نَمُوتُ وَإِلَيْكَ الْمَصِيرُ), ''ya Allah ! hamney teri inayat sey Sham ki, aur teri tofiq sey subah ki, aur teri qudrat sey hum zinda hain aur teri qudrat hi sey mareingey, aur teri taraf hi wapis jana hai.''"
3869,"Hazrat Aban bin Usman bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey suna , wo farma rahey they : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jo banda har din ki subah ko aur har raat ki Sham ko teen baar ye dua padhey usey koi chiz nuqsan nahin pahunchaeygi : (بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الَّذِي لَا يَضُرُّ مَعَ اسْمِهِ شَيْءٌ فِي الْأَرْضِ وَلَا فِي السَّمَاءِ وَهُوَ السَّمِيعُ الْعَلِيمُ ), ''Allah key naam key zariey sey (panah maangta hun) jis key naam ki barkat sey zamin aur aasman mein koi chiz nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakti aur wo khub sunney wala khub janney wala hai."" Raavi kehtey hain : Hazrat Aban (Rahimahullah) key jism par faalij ka asar tha, chunanche (un sey hadees sunney wala) aadmi un ki taraf (tajjub sey) dekhney laga. Hazrat Aban (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : meri taraf kya dekhtey ho? hadees isi tarah hai jaisey mainey tujhey sunai hai, lekin us din mainey ye dua nahin padhi thi, is tarah Allah ney apna faisla mujh par jari farma diya."
3870,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key khaadim Hazrat Abu-Salaam sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo musalman, ya jo insan, ya jo banda Sham key waqt aur subah key waqt yun kehta hai : (رَضِيتُ بِاللَّهِ رَبًّا , وَبِالْإِسْلَامِ دِينًا , وَبِمُحَمَّدٍ نَبِيًّا), ''main Allah key Rab honey par, Islam key Deen honey par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Nabi honey par razi hun.''  to Allah Taala qiyamat key din usey lazimi tor par razi karega."
3871,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) subah aur Sham ye duayen padhna tarak nahin farmatey they : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي . . . . . . وَأَعُوذُبِكَ أَنْ أُغْتَالَ مِنْ تَحْتِي), ''ya Allah ! be-shak mein tujh sey duniya aur aakhirat mein maafi aur aafiyat ka sawal karta hun, ya Allah ! beshak main tujh sey maafi ka aur Deen aur duniya mein ehal aur ayaal aur maal aur asbab mein aafiyat ka sawal karta hun, ya Allah ! merey aibon par parda dal dey aur meri pareshaaniyon sey mujhey aman dey. aur meri hifazat farma merey samney sey, merey peechhey sey, meri daain taraf sey, meri baain taraf sey aur merey ooper sey, aur main is baat sey bhi teri panah mein aata hun ke mujhey nichey sey achcha pakad liya jaey.'' Imam Wakee (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke is sey murad zamin mein dhans jana hai."
3872,"Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (اللَّهُمَّ أَنْتَ رَبِّي لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا أَنْتَ , خَلَقْتَنِي وَأَنَا عَبْدُكَ , وَأَنَا عَلَى عَهْدِكَ وَوَعْدِكَ maa اسْتَطَعْتُ , أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنْ شَرِّ maa صَنَعْتُ , أَبُوءُ بِنِعْمَتِكَ , وَأَبُوءُ بِذَنْبِي فَاغْفِرْلِي , فَإِنَّهُ لَا يَغْفِرُ الذُّنُوبَ إِلَّا أَنْتَ), ''aey Allah ! to mera Rab hai, terey siwa koi mabood nahin. tu ney mujhey paida kiya aur main tera banda hun aur apni taqat key mutabiq main terey ehad aur wadey par qaaim hun. main apney aamaal key shar sey teri panah mein aataa hun. main teri nemat ka iqrar karta hun, (jo mujh par hai) aur apney gunah ka bhi aetraaf karta hun, lihaza mujhey bakhsh dey. haqiqat ye hai ke terey siwa koi bhi gunahon ko maaf nahin kar sakta.'' Raavi hadees bayan kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney din key waqt ya raat key waqt ye dua padhi , phir isi din ya usi raat faut ho gaya to wo Inshallah Taala jannat mein jaeyga."
3873,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat kartey huye farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bistar par tashrif ley jatey to farmatey : (اللَّهُمَّ ! رَبَّ السَّمَوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضِ . . . وَأَغْنِنِي مِنَ الْفَقْرِ), ''aey Allah ! aey aasmano aur zamin key Malik ! aur har chiz key Malik ! aey daney aur guthli ko phadney waley ! aey Toraat, Injeel aur Quran Azeem ko nazil farmaney waley ! main har us jaan daar key shar sey teri panah mein aata hun jiski peshani terey qabzey mein hai. to hi awwal hai, tujh sey pehley kuchh nahin . to hi aakhir hai, terey baad kuchh nahin. to hi zahir hai, tujh sey ooper kuchh nahin. to hi baatin hai, tujh sey poshida tar koi chiz nahin. mujh sey mera qarz ada kar dey aur mujhey faqr sey (najat dey kar) ghani kar dey.''"
3874,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs bistar par letnaa chahey to wo apney tehband ka kinara khol kar uskey sath apney bistar ko jhaad ley kyonkey usey malum nahin ke uski ghair mojudgi mein us (bistar) par kya chiz aai, phir apney daain pehlu let kar yun kahey : (رَبِّ ! بِكَ وَضَعْتُ جَنْبِي . . عِبَادَكَ الصَّالِحِينَ), ''aey merey Rab ! teri hi tofiq sey mainey apna pehlu (bistar par) rakha hai aur teri hi tofiq sey isey uthaaoonga. agar tu ney meri rooh (is doran mein) qabz kar li to is par reham farmana, aur agar to isey chhod dey (aur qabz na karey) to iski is tareeqey sey hifazat farmana jaisey to apney nek bandon ki hifazat farmata hai.''"
3875,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bistar par aaram farma hotey to muawwizatain (Sura- Falaq aur Sura- Naas) padh kar apney haathon par phunk maartey aur phir dono haath jism Mubarak par pher letey."
3876,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi sey farmaya : jab to soney lagey, ya farmaya : jab to apney bistar par jaey to keh : (اللَّهُمَّ أَسْلَمْتُ وَجْهِي إِلَيْكَ . . وَنَبِيِّكَ الَّذِي أَرْسَلْتَ), ''aey Allah ! mainey apna chehra terey tabey kar diya, aur apni pusht teri taraf jhukaai, aur apna maamla terey supurd kar diya, sawab mein raghbat (dilchaspi) kartey huye aur terey azab sey dartey huye. teri bargah key siwa koi thikana aur jaey panah nahin. main teri is Kitab par eman laya jo tu ney nazil ki, aur terey us Nabi par eman laya jisey tu ney bheja.'' phir agar to is raat mein faut ho gaya to teri maut fitrat (deen Islam) par hogi, aur agar tujhey (khairiyat sey) subah ho gaee to teri ye subah is haal mein hogi ke to bahut bhalai hasil kar chuka hoga."
3877,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bistar par tashrif ley jatey to apna daayan haath apney rukhsaar key nichey rakh kar farmatey : (اللهم ! , قِنِي عَذَابَكَ يَوْمَ تَبْعَثُ عِبَادَكَ) ya farmatey (يوم تجمع عبادك ), ''aey Allah ! mujhey (us din) apney azab sey mehfooz rakhna jis din to apney bandon ko uthaeyga. ya apney bandon ko jama kerega.''"
3878,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ki raat ko aankh khul gaee aur usney jaag kar yun kaha : (لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ , لَهُ الْمُلْكُ , وَلَهُ الْحَمْدُ , وَهُوَ عَلَى كُلِّ شَيْءٍ قَدِيرٌ , سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ , وَالْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ , وَلَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ , وَاللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ , وَلَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّةَ إِلَّا بِاللَّهِ الْعَلِيِّ الْعَظِيمِ), ''akeley Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin, uska koi shareek nahin, badshahi usi ki hai, aur usi key liye sab tareef hai aur wo har chiz par kamil qudrat rakhta hai. Allah paak hai aur sab tareef Allah hi key liye hai, aur Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin. aur Allah sab sey bada hai. aur bulandiyon aur azmaton waley Allah ki madad key baghair na burai sey bachao mumkin hai na neki ki taqat.'' phir iskey baad usney ye dua ki : (رَبِّ اغْفِرْلِي ), ''aey merey Rab ! mujhey bakhsh dey."" to uski bakhshish ho jaeygi. (Raavi hadees) Waleed bin Muslim bayan kartey hain ke ya aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney yun farmaya : phir dua karta hai to uski dua qubul ho jati hai. agar uth kar wuzu karta hai, phir namaz padhta hai to uski namaz qubul hoti hai."
3879,"Hazrat Rabeea bin Kaab Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key darwazey key qarib raat guzaartey they. wo raat key waqt Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kafi der tak ye padhtey huye suntey : ( سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ ), ''tamam jahano ka Malik Allah pak hai.'' phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : (سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ وَبِحَمْدِهِ), ''paak hai Allah apni khoobiyon aur ta'reefon samet.''"
3880,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab raat ko jaagtey to farmatey : (الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ الَّذِي أَحْيَانَا بَعْدَ ما أَمَاتَنَا وَإِلَيْهِ النُّشُورُ), ''Allah ka shukar hai jisney hamein maut deney key baad zindagi bakhsh di aur usi ki taraf uth kar jana hai.''"
3881,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo banda baa wuzu sota hai, phir raat ko uski aankh khulti hai to wo Allah sey duniya key maamlat mein sey ya aakhirat key maamlat mein sey kisi chiz ka sawal karta hai to Allah usey wo chiz dey deta hai."
3882,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar Taiyaar (Raziallahu anhuma) apni walida Hazrat Asma binte Umes (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney pareshani key moqey par padhney key liye mujhey ye alfaz sikhaey : (اللَّهُ , اللَّهُ رَبِّي لَا أُشْرِكُ بِهِ شَيْئًا), ''Allah, sirf Allah mera Rab hai, main uskey sath kisi ko shareek nahin karti.''"
3883,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pareshani key waqt ye dua padha kartey they : (لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ الْحَلِيمُ الْكَرِيمُ , سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَرْشِ الْعَظِيمِ , سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ رَبِّ السَّمَوَاتِ السَّبْعِ , وَرَبِّ الْعَرْشِ الْكَرِيمِ), ''Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin jo nihayat burdbar (samajhdar) aur bahut ziyada sakhi hai. Allah paak hai jo arsh azeem ka Malik hai. aur Allah paak hai jo saat aasmano ka Malik aur izzat waley arsh ka Malik hai.'' (Raavi hadees) Wakee ney eik martaba aakhiri do jumlon mein ''Subhan Allah'' ke bajaey ''لا اله الا الله"" key alfaz bayan kiye hain."
3884,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ghar sey bahar tashrif ley jatey to farmatey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُ بِكَ أَنْ أَضِلَّ , أَوْ أَزِلَّ , أَوْ أَظْلِمَ أَوْ أُظْلَمَ , أَوْ أَجْهَلَ أَوْ يُجْهَلَ عَلَيَّ ), ''ya Allah ! main (is baat sey) teri panah mein aata hun ke main gumrah ho jaun ya main laghzish ka shikar ho jaun, ya main kisi par zulm karun ya mujh par koi zulm karey, ya main kisi sey bad-tameezi karun ya koi mujh sey bad-tameezi sey pesh aaye.''"
3885,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ghar sey bahar tashrif ley jatey to farmatey : ( بِسْمِ اللَّهِ , لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّةَ إِلَّا بِاللَّهِ , التُّكْلَانُ عَلَى اللَّهِ ), ''(miin is ghar sey) Allah key naam key sath (nikal raha hun), Allah ki tofiq key baghair na burai sey bachao mumkin hai na neki ki taqat, Allah hi par bharosa hai.''"
3886,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab aadmi apney ghar key darwazey sey bahar nikalta hai to uskey sath do farishtey hotey hain jo uskey sath muqarrar hain. jab wo kehta hai : (بِسْمِ اللَّهِ) wo kehtey hain : tujhey hidayat mil gaee. jab wo kehta hai : (لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّةَ إِلَّا بِاللَّهِ ) to wo kehtey hain : teri hifazat ho gaee. jab wo kehta hai : ( تَوَكَّلْتُ عَلَى اللَّهِ ) to wo kehtey hain : to (Allah key siwa) dusron sey be-niyaz ho gaya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir usey uskey (sath rehney waley) do shetan miltey hain to wo dono (aapas mein) kehtey hain is shakhs sey tum kya chahtey ho jiski rehnumai ki gaee , jisey be niyazi hasil ho gaee aur jis ko (hum sey) mehfooz kar diya gaya?"
3887,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap ney farmaya : jab aadmi apney ghar mein dakhil hota hai aur dakhil hotey waqt aur khana khatey waqt Allah ka naam leta hai to shetan (apney sathiyon sey) kehta hai : tumharey liye (yahan) na raat guzarney ki jagah hai na raat ka khana hai. aur jab wo ghar mein dakhil hotey waqt Allah ka naam na ley to shetan (apney sathiyon sey) kehta hai : tumhen raat guzarney ki jagah mil gaee. aur jab khana khatey waqt bhi Allah ka naam na ley to wo kehta hai : tumhen raat guzarney ko thikana bhi mil gaya aur raat ka khana bhi mil gaya."
3888,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Sarjis (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab safar ikhtiyar farmatey to kehtey aur (Raavi hadees) Abdur-Raheem ney kaha : (in alfaz key zariey sey) panah maangtey : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنْ وَعْثَاءِ السَّفَرِ , وَكَآبَةِ الْمُنْقَلَبِ , وَالْحَوْرِ بَعْدَ الْكَوْرِ , وَدَعْوَةِ الْمَظْلُومِ , وَسُوءِ الْمَنْظَرِ فِي الْأَهْلِ وَالْمَالِ), ''ya Allah ! main safar ki mashaqqat sey, pareshankun wapsi sey, kamaal key baad tanazzul sey, mazloom ki bad-dua sey aur ehal aur ayaal aur maal mein buri soorate-haal nazar aaney sey teri panah mein aata hun.'' Raavi hadees Abu-Muaawia ye izafa bhi bayan kartey hain : aur jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safar sey wapis tashrif latey to yehi dua padhtey."
3889,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi ufuq sey badal aata dekhtey to jis kaam mein bhi mashghool hotey, chahey namaz hi mein kyon na hotey, usey chhod kar badal ki taraf mutawajjeh ho jatey aur farmatey : (اللهم إِنَّا نَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنْ شَرِّ ما أُرْسِلَ بِهِ), ''ya Allah ! hum us chiz key shar sey teri panah mein aatey hain jo kuchh dey kar ye (badal) bheja gaya hai.'' agar barish shuru ho jati to do baar ya teen baar farmatey :  (اللَّهُمَّ صَيِّبًا نَافِعًا), ''ya Allah ! is barish ko faeyde-mand bana dey.'' agar barish na hoti aur Allah Taala badal ko hata deta to aap Allah ka shukar kartey."
3890,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab barish dekhtey to farmatey : (اللَّهُمَّ ! اجْعَلْهُ صَيِّبًا هَنِيئًا), ''ya Allah ! is barish ko nafa bakhsh khushgawar bana dey.''"
3891,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab ghata dekhtey to aap key chehre Mubarak ka rang badal jata. aap kabhi andar tashrif ley jatey, kabhi bahar tashrif ley aatey. kabhi (eik taraf) aatey. kabhi (doosri taraf) jatey, phir jab barish honey lagti to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki pareshani door ho jati. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jo kaifiyat mehsus ki thi, wo aap ki khidmat mein arz ki (ke aap ki ye kaifiyat kyon hoti hai)? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tujhey kya maloom? shayad ye wesa hi badal ho jaisey Hud (Alaihissalam) ki qom ney (eik badal dekh kar) kaha tha : (aur Allah Taala ney Quran Majeed mein unka tazkira kartey huye farmaya : (فَلَمَّا رأَوْهُ عَارِضًا مُّسْتَقْبِلَ أَوْدِيَتِهِمْ قَالُوا هَـٰذَا عَارِضٌ مُّمْطِرُنَا بَلْ هُوَ ما ٱسْتَعْجَلْتُم بِهِ), ''jab unhoney us azab ko badal ki surat main apni wadiyon ki taraf aatey huye dekha to boley : ye badal hum par barish barsaney wala hai, (Hood (Alaihissalam) ney kaha : nahin) balke ye to wo azab hai jiski tum jaldi kar rahey they."
3892,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis ko achcha koi musibat zada mil jaey aur wo (dekhney wala) ye dua padh ley : (الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ الَّذِي عَافَانِي مِمَّا ابْتَلَاكَ بِهِ , وَفَضَّلَنِي عَلَى كَثِيرٍ مِمَّنْ خَلَقَ تَفْضِيلًا), ''har qism ki tareef us Allah key liye hai jisney mujhey is musibat sey aafiyat mein rakha jis mein tujhey mubtala kiya hai, aur apney paida kiye huye bahut sey bandon par usney mujhey fazilat ata farmaai.'' to wo is musibat sey mehfooz rahega, chahey koi si musibat ho."
